NAME
    MojoX::JsonConfig - parse Mojolicious json configuration files without
    web app.

SYNOPSIS
        use MojoX::JsonConfig;

        my $config = parse_config_file 'myapp.json';

DESCRIPTION
    MojoX::JsonConfig parse Mojolicious json configuration files without web
    app.

  "parse_config"
        my $config = parse_config($config_content);

    Parse configuration from variable $config_content.

  "parse_config_file"
        my $config = parse_config_file($config_file);

    Parse configuration file $config_file.

SEE ALSO
    Mojolicious::Plugin::JsonConfig

